        Is French an easy language to learn?
        _________ French is _________ easy language to learn. French is the name of a language. Therefore, no article shall be used in the first blank while in the second blank ,'an' is used because it is followed with the word 'easy'. 'French is an easy language to learn.' Option B)No article required , an is the correct option.

        How do I become a good French speaker?
        To become a natural and confident French speaker, train yourself to think in French first.
